      "writtenOn": "2020-08-27T16:06:32Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Since the C++ version is always in *some API flux, let\u0027s always include Julia when we want to expose something into JS",
      "revId": "abbae2511d55085dfc1455ddc225a4ef2d1c97d7",
